    <div class="row">
        <div class="one-half column infobox">
          <h3>How It Works</h3>
          <p>With Local Tokens, when you provide someone a good or service, 
            they agree to give you a certain number of (virtual) tokens. 
            They transfer the tokens to you online. 
            When you want to access a good or service from someone else, 
            you transfer tokens from your account to theirs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="one-half column infobox">
          
