          <h3>Join Us</h3>
          <p>When you sign up for an account, you get 2 tokens to start off. 
            You can also earn tokens by helping maintain the community, like moderating disputes, or chipping in for server fees. (More about that <a>here</a>.)</p> 
            <p>You'll have access to our listings of what people have to offer, and of course, you can always trade with people you already know.  Sign up &rarr; </p>
          
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="one-half column infobox">
          <h3>Community Values</h3>
          <p>Trading locally keeps resources in the community. Local Tokens are based on time, not money, and we run on the principle that no one's time is more valuable than anyone else's. Though you could try to assign a dollar amount to time, we choose not to, and Local Tokens are never redeemable for cash. A good way to think about the value of Local Tokens is that one token is roughly equal to one hour of a person's time. How many hours is your neighbor's couch worth? That's up to you and your neighbor to decide.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="one-half column infobox">
          
        </div>
    </div>

