            <h4>So it's bartering?</h4>
            <p>No. It's much easier. To barter, you have to find a person who both has something
             you want and wants something you have. With Local Tokens, you
             exchange tokens, like you would cash, so that everyone gets what they actually need.</p>

            <h4>So it's just money?</h4>
            <p>It's currency, but not money. Local Tokens have no cash value. 
